item.title: CVE-2021-3708|2024-08-03T17:01:07.839Z -- d-link -- dsl-2750u
item.description: D-Link router DSL-2750U with firmware vME1.16 or prior versions is vulnerable to OS command injection. An unauthenticated attacker on the local network may exploit this, with CVE-2021-3707, to execute any OS commands on the vulnerable device.

item.title: CVE-2021-3707|2024-08-03T17:01:07.681Z -- d-link -- dsl-2750u
item.description: D-Link router DSL-2750U with firmware vME1.16 or prior versions is vulnerable to unauthorized configuration modification. An unauthenticated attacker on the local network may exploit this, with CVE-2021-3708, to execute any OS commands on the vulnerable device.
